des:
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.

After connecting Alexa to your Kruidvat Smart Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Kruidvat Smart Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in our “Kruidvat Smart Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Kruidvat Smart Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Kruidvat Smart Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Kruidvat Smart Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search " Kruidvat Smart Home " skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of " Kruidvat Smart Home ", and you'll be navigated to Kruidvat Smart Home login page;
(9). Input your Kruidvat Smart Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
